WEBVTT

00:01.043 --> 00:03.420
You're dying and it's eating me up inside.

00:03.420 --> 00:04.588
So? Are we okay?

00:04.630 --> 00:06.340
You're going off like a dog aren't you?

00:06.340 --> 00:07.214
What do you mean?

00:07.214 --> 00:09.176
When a dog knows it's gonna die he

00:09.176 --> 00:10.510
goes off into the woods by itself.

00:10.510 --> 00:11.503
Denny got engaged.

00:11.503 --> 00:12.461
Who is it this time?

00:12.461 --> 00:13.471
Beverly Bridge.

00:13.506 --> 00:14.688
You think I'm screwing

00:14.688 --> 00:16.309
Denny for his money and power?

00:16.309 --> 00:17.498
It had occurred to me.

00:17.498 --> 00:20.269
I'm prepared to give you $500,000 right now

00:20.304 --> 00:21.876
if you walk away and never have any

00:21.876 --> 00:23.378
contact with Denny Crane ever again.

00:23.378 --> 00:25.630
Bev turned down the offer that I made her.

00:25.630 --> 00:28.022
<i>She was very offended.</i>

00:28.057 --> 00:30.414
<i>This is going to get ugly.</i>

